    "image_with_text_YmjFkV": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_VpJWcw": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Bathroom Tapware: The Finishing Touch of Luxury",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_n3Ehkw": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Refine your bathroom with high-quality tapware that pairs aesthetic appeal with everyday performance. At Cook & Bathe, our extensive range of bathroom tapware includes basin mixers, bath spouts, wall mixers, and shower tapware available in stylish finishes like matte black, brushed gold, brushed nickel, and chrome - ideal for modern, classic, or minimalist interiors.</p><p>We stock premium brands renowned for their quality, innovation, and design versatility:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/phoenix\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/phoenix\">Phoenix Tapware</a> – Sleek, elegant designs crafted for the demands of Australian bathrooms</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/hansgrohe\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/hansgrohe\">Hansgrohe</a> – German-engineered tapware offering cutting-edge form and water-saving functionality</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bella-vista-1\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bella-vista-1\">Bella Vista</a> – Affordable, high-style bathroom tapware with contemporary finishes</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bourne\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bourne\">Bourne</a> – Practical yet stylish tapware options designed for everyday Australian homes</p><p>Whether you’re designing a new bathroom or upgrading your fixtures, our designer bathroom taps deliver reliability, visual harmony, and efficient water flow.</p><p>Explore the full bathroom tapware collection online or visit our showroom to experience our curated selection in person.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_nCzpwi": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop Bathroom Tapware",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/tapware-bathroom"
          }
        }
      },
