    "image_with_text_dLeNVc": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_CMMNXA": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Bathroom Basins: Style That Starts at the Sink",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_n8gDHM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Enhance your bathroom with a premium basin that combines beautiful design with everyday practicality. At Cook & Bathe, our wide selection of bathroom basins caters to all interior styles and space requirements - from minimalist powder rooms to luxurious master ensuites. Crafted from durable materials and available in a variety of shapes and finishes, our basins are designed to complement modern and classic bathrooms alike.</p><p>Choose from a variety of functional and stylish basin types:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/above-counter\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/above-counter\">Above Counter Basins</a> – A popular choice for contemporary bathrooms, these basins sit proudly on top of the vanity to create a bold visual statement. Available in round, oval, square, and rectangular shapes.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/under-counter\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/under-counter\">Under Counter Basins</a> – Installed beneath the benchtop for a sleek, integrated look. These basins offer a smooth surface and are ideal for minimalist spaces.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/inset\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/inset\">Inset Basins</a> – Partially recessed into the vanity, inset basins provide the best of both worlds—clean lines and a subtle design feature that suits many bathroom styles.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-hung-basins\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-hung-basins\">Wall Hung Basins</a> – A space-saving solution perfect for small bathrooms, powder rooms, and ensuites. These basins are mounted directly to the wall for a floating, modern effect.</p><p>Whether you’re renovating, building new, or simply upgrading your vanity, our range of designer bathroom basins ensures durability, ease of maintenance, and a refined finish.</p><p>Explore our full collection online or visit our showroom to find the perfect basin for your next bathroom project.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_7XpRcQ": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Explore Basins",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/basins-and-sinks"
          }
        }
      },
