    "image_with_text_HEmJMW": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Jkt4NN": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Showers: Elevate Your Everyday Ritual",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_GFWUpd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Upgrade your bathroom with a stylish and functional shower system that enhances your daily routine. At Cook & Bathe, our extensive range of showers includes everything from minimalist designs to luxurious twin shower systems - perfect for every type of bathroom and lifestyle. Whether you’re planning a full renovation or simply updating your fixtures, our shower solutions offer comfort, performance, and visual appeal.</p><p>Explore our collection of premium shower types:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/rail-showers\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/rail-showers\">Rail Showers</a> – Adjustable and practical, rail showers are ideal for shared bathrooms or households with varying height requirements. Slide the shower head along the rail to customise your experience and enjoy flexible water delivery.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/twin-showers\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/twin-showers\">Twin Showers</a> – Designed for luxury and versatility, twin showers combine an overhead rain shower with a detachable hand shower. Enjoy the best of both worlds with this all-in-one setup - ideal for family bathrooms or spa-style ensuites.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/shower-heads\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/shower-heads\">Shower Heads</a> – Create a relaxing escape with our range of fixed shower heads, available in round or square styles and multiple finishes. From ultra-modern ceiling-mounted designs to wall-mounted classics, find the perfect piece to match your aesthetic.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/hand-showers\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/hand-showers\">Hand Showers</a> – Offering convenience and flexibility, handheld showers are perfect for targeted washing, rinsing, or cleaning. Pair them with wall brackets or rail systems for added functionality and easy control.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/domus-living\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/domus-living\">Shower Floors by Domus Living</a> – Finish your space with high-quality shower floors designed by Domus Living. These bases offer durability, slip resistance, and a sleek appearance that works seamlessly with frameless or semi-frameless enclosures. Ideal for creating a clean, low-profile shower zone.</p><p>Whether you’re designing a modern wet room or a classic family bathroom, our shower collection provides everything you need to build a beautiful and highly functional space.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_Ga6L8m": {
