    "image_with_text_9dBPy7": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_7nb9pW": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Toilets: Comfort, Innovation & Clean Design",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_APqfWz": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Upgrade your bathroom with our premium range of toilets designed for modern Australian living. At Cook & Bathe, we offer a variety of styles to suit every space, from minimalist powder rooms to luxury ensuites. Combining water efficiency, sleek design, and hygienic features, our toilet collection delivers both form and function.</p><p>Explore our most popular toilet types:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/smart-toilets\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/smart-toilets\">Smart Toilets</a> – Experience the future of bathroom comfort with advanced features like bidet functionality, heated seats, and automatic flushing. Perfect for those who value hygiene and innovation.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/back-to-wall-toilets\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/back-to-wall-toilets\">Back to Wall Toilets</a> – With the cistern concealed within the wall or a vanity unit, these toilets offer a clean, streamlined look and are easy to maintain.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-faced\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-faced\">Wall Faced Toilets</a> – Designed to sit flush against the wall, wall faced toilets provide a neat finish while hiding pipework for a clutter-free appearance.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-hung-toilets\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-hung-toilets\">Wall Hung Toilets</a> – Ideal for space-saving layouts, wall hung toilets are mounted directly to the wall with a concealed cistern, creating a modern, floating effect that’s easy to clean beneath.</p><p>Crafted by trusted brands and built for long-term performance, our toilets combine cutting-edge design with reliable functionality.</p><p>Browse the full toilet collection online or visit our showroom to find the perfect solution for your bathroom project.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_nPVfY7": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
