    "image_with_text_MwjKV4": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_D9fUY8": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Baths: The Centrepiece of Relaxation",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_kDEd9j": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Transform your bathroom into a luxurious retreat with Cook & Bathe’s curated collection of premium baths. Whether you’re creating a spa-inspired sanctuary or updating a functional family space, our selection offers comfort, quality, and timeless style. Designed to suit a variety of bathroom layouts, our baths are available in a range of sizes, shapes, and finishes to elevate any interior.</p><p>Explore our most popular bath styles:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/freestanding-bath-tubs\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/freestanding-bath-tubs\">Freestanding Baths</a> – Make a bold design statement with a freestanding bath, perfect for open-plan bathrooms and luxury renovations. With sculptural forms and elegant curves, these baths become the focal point of any space - ideal for soaking, relaxing, and unwinding.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/inset-baths\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/inset-baths\">Inset Baths</a> – Built into a hob or surround, inset baths are a classic choice for both modern and traditional bathrooms. Their sleek integration into your cabinetry or tiled space offers a clean, seamless look that’s easy to maintain and space-efficient.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/back-to-wall\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/back-to-wall\">Back to Wall Baths</a> – Offering the visual impact of a freestanding bath with the practicality of wall installation, back-to-wall baths sit flush against the wall to maximise space and simplify cleaning. These baths are perfect for smaller bathrooms or streamlined layouts without compromising on design impact.</p><p>Each bath in our collection is crafted from durable, high-quality materials that retain heat and resist wear - ensuring long-lasting performance and comfort. With options to suit minimalist, coastal, or contemporary interiors, you’ll find the perfect bath to match your vision.</p><p>Shop the full range of baths online or visit our Melbourne showrooms to experience our collection in person. Whether you’re designing a master ensuite or upgrading a family bathroom, Cook & Bathe helps you bathe beautifully.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_TpTkCJ": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Discover Baths",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/baths"
