    "image_with_text_D4pneR": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Fm8WkK": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Bathroom Vanities: Style, Storage & Sophistication",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_LTFPD8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Complete your bathroom with a designer vanity that combines everyday functionality with timeless style. At Cook & Bathe, our collection of bathroom vanities is crafted to meet the demands of modern Australian living - offering practical storage, beautiful finishes, and quality construction. Whether you’re furnishing a compact ensuite or designing a luxurious main bathroom, our range includes sizes, styles, and configurations to suit every space.</p><p>Choose from top-tier brands known for quality and innovation:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/otti\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/otti\">Otti</a> – Sleek, contemporary vanities in matte and timber-look finishes, featuring soft-close drawers, integrated basins, and space-saving designs ideal for modern homes.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/pages/timberline-range\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/pages/timberline-range\">Timberline</a> – Proudly Australian made, Timberline vanities offer fully customisable options with premium materials, solid surface tops, and smart storage solutions. Ideal for those seeking both beauty and durability.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza\">Fienza</a> – Affordable, functional vanities with clean lines and versatile design. Perfect for budget-friendly renovations that don’t compromise on quality or aesthetics.</p><p>Our bathroom vanities are available in wall-hung, floor-standing, and double-basin formats, with a wide range of finishes including classic white, natural oak, matte black, and more. Many styles come with matching mirrors or mirrored shaving cabinets to create a complete and cohesive look.</p><p>Explore our full collection of vanities online or visit our Melbourne showrooms to speak with our experienced consultants and find the perfect piece for your bathroom.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_jTatKj": {
