          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Bathroom Accessories: Refined Details That Complete Your Space",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_LhaDhc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Finish your bathroom with elegant, functional accessories that elevate both style and usability. At Cook & Bathe, our curated range of bathroom accessories brings cohesion, convenience, and luxury to your space - proving that the smallest details often make the biggest impact. Whether you’re renovating or upgrading, our collection is designed to complement modern and traditional bathrooms alike.</p><p>Explore a wide selection of essential accessories including:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/towel-rail\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/towel-rail\">Towel Rails & Rings</a> – Available in single, double, and heated styles, our towel rails offer everyday practicality while matching your chosen tapware finish for a seamless look.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/toilet-roll-holder\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/toilet-roll-holder\">Toilet Roll Holders</a> – A must-have for every bathroom, these fixtures come in sleek minimalist styles or more traditional forms to match your space.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/robe-hook\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/robe-hook\">Robe Hooks</a> – Compact yet functional, robe hooks keep garments and towels off the floor, adding order to your layout without compromising aesthetics.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/soap-dish-dispenser\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/soap-dish-dispenser\">Soap Dishes & Dispensers</a> – Keep your vanity area organised and hygienic with wall-mounted or bench-top options that suit any bathroom style.</p><p>Available in a variety of finishes such as chrome, brushed nickel, brushed gold, and matte black, our bathroom accessories are designed to coordinate with your tapware, basin, and other fittings - bringing balance and visual consistency to your bathroom.</p><p>Shop the full bathroom accessories range online or visit our Melbourne showrooms to explore the collection in person and complete your space with lasting style.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_7yrjNp": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Discover Bathroom Accessories",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/accessories-bathroom"
          }
        }
      },
